{"arkId":"cl010093387","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010093387","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Fragment de torse d\u0027homme \u00e0 demi-nu","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Fragment de torse d\u0027homme \u00e0 demi-nu"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1240 - 1260","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1240,"endYear":1260,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"France \u00cele-de-France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 1002 A","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"haut relief fragment","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0,27","displayDimension":"0,27 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,27","displayDimension":"0,27 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,265","displayDimension":"0,265 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"pierre calcaire","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"jub\u00e9 (France-\u003EParis-\u003Ecath\u00e9drale-\u003ENotre-Dame)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Provient du jub\u00e9 de la cath\u00e9drale Notre-Dame de Paris, consacr\u00e9 \u00e0 la Passion. Peut-\u00eatre identifi\u00e9 \u00e0 une figure de Christ en croix. El\u00e9ment possible d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne de crucifixion plac\u00e9e sous la croix triomphale ou vestige de cette croix. Ensemble \u00e9rig\u00e9 au XIIIe si\u00e8cle, masqu\u00e9 entre 1627 et 1636 lors de la reconstruction de l\u0027autel de la Vierge, voulue par Anne d\u0027Autriche, puis d\u00e9truit apr\u00e8s 1699 lors des travaux de transformation du choeur accomplis par Jules-Hardouin Mansart et Robert de Cotte, en ex\u00e9cution du voeu de Louis XIII. Fragment enfoui sous le dallage du choeur, retrouv\u00e9 en 1858 lors des travaux d\u0027Eug\u00e8ne Viollet-le-Duc. D\u00e9p\u00f4t lapidaire de Notre-Dame de Paris. Attribu\u00e9 au mus\u00e9e du Louvre en 1894 (comit\u00e9s des 12 juillet 1894 et 11 octobre 1894, autorisation du ministre de l\u0027Int\u00e9rieur transmise par le ministre de l\u0027Instruction Publique et des Beaux-Arts le 27 juin 1894)","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"affect\u00e9 au Louvre","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"autres dates","value":"27\/06\/1894","startYear":1894,"endYear":1894},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"12\/07\/1894","startYear":1894,"endYear":1894},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"11\/10\/1894","startYear":1894,"endYear":1894}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"affect\u00e9 au Louvre"}],"material":[{"value":"pierre calcaire"}],"place":[{"value":"jub\u00e9"}],"objectType":[{"value":"haut relief fragment"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Bern\u00e9, Damien (dir.), Faire parler les pierres. Sculptures m\u00e9di\u00e9vales de Notre-Dame de Paris, cat. exp. (Paris (Externe, France), Mus\u00e9e du Moyen-Age et Thermes de Cluny, 2024), Dijon, Faton, 2024","bibliographyDate":"2024","bibliographyDetail":"p. 165, p. 165, Cat. 26d","compar